t = int(input())
while t:
    t = t - 1
    (l, r, g) = map(int, input().split())
    x1 = l % g
    if x1 == 0:
        b1 = l // g
    else:
        x = g - x1
        b1 = (l + x) // g
    x = r % g
    b2 = (r - x) // g
    temp = b2 - b1 + 1
    if temp == 1 and b2 != 1:
        print('0')
    else:
        print(b2 - b1 + 1)

n = int(input())
for i in range(0, n):
    p = input().rstrip().split(' ')
    T = p[0:2]
    T.sort(key=int)
    l = int(T[0])
    r = int(T[1])
    g = int(p[2])
    A = r // g
    B = (l - 1) // g
